Zero point energy                ...      0.38818019 Eh     243.59 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.02442750 Eh      15.33 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
